Bower.

    Bower is the Automation tool used to download the Required Resources to develop web applications

    Ex.

        Bootstrap

        jQuery

        AngularJS

            --
            --
            --

    Bower is the Automation tool given by the NodeJS.


bower_components.

1.bower.json

{

    "name":"nareshit",
    "dependencies":{
        "bootstrap":"~3.3.6",
        "angular":"~1.6.0"
    }

}



2. .bowerrc


{
    "directory":"bower_components"
